Here we provide a simple script ending with .az extention, which content can be anything, in unicode, basically any natural language. It can also contain pictures, but you have to provide the link anyway. It is pure text, interpretable by the lazero program.

Everytime one wants to run something indefinitely, if described well, the program will just go for it forever. So you might want to limit the time. Note that the timer will not work if there hasn't been one.
